Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.43,0:02:12.80,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\an8\fs21\be1}第七回  「信奈上洛」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.62,0:02:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁戴將軍上洛的計劃泡湯了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.72,0:02:20.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軍雖然被暗殺了  但是還有弟弟義昭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.77,0:02:23.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把義昭奉為新的將軍的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.42,0:02:25.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就有上洛的大義名分了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:29.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰被暗殺了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.74,0:02:32.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了是將軍足利義輝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.29,0:02:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,義輝公沒有被暗殺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.01,0:02:35.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:38.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不是弟弟  是妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.26,0:02:39.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.13,0:02:43.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲的事件應該是將軍被暗殺…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.40,0:02:46.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軍在千鈞一髮之際逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.03,0:02:50.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和妹妹義昭大人一起逃往大陸了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.96,0:02:52.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.42,0:02:57.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歷史要是走向我不知道的岔路的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:02:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的存在價值就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.31,0:03:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猴子要從樹上掉下來咯  猴子前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.52,0:03:08.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我來代替連猴子的智慧都沒有了的相良前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.67,0:03:10.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發表一個好提案
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:15.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被織田家抓住的今川義元
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:16.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有足利家的血脈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.27,0:03:19.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有繼承將軍家的資格
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.71,0:03:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把今川義元奉為下一任將軍上洛就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:33.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯嘛  不枉我讓你加入織田家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:35.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追上相良前輩並超越他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.02,0:03:37.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:38.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.38,0:03:42.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼織田軍開始上洛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.57,0:03:43.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.89,0:03:50.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,途中有淺井和六角等強敵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.18,0:03:56.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.98,0:03:59.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也真夠纏人的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.36,0:04:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織田和淺井應該結盟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.50,0:04:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不想和淺井為敵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.27,0:04:10.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啊  為敵又怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.62,0:04:12.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.05,0:04:15.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  怕的是你那邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.63,0:04:18.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟到處宣揚要結婚了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.10,0:04:21.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是在這裡被取消婚事的話就成天下人的笑柄了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.98,0:04:23.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.89,0:04:27.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過呢  你要是哭著求我  也許可以考慮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.71,0:04:29.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.61,0:04:31.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  這事就當沒發生過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:34.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.72,0:04:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不能結婚的話  我就回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:39.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當幫幫我  請一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:41.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.06,0:04:45.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的妹妹嫁給你好了  感謝我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.57,0:04:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:51.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有聽說過信奈大人有妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.26,0:04:53.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…有啦  說有就有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:55.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是再囉嗦就取消婚事咯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.35,0:04:59.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跪求您妹！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:04.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  信長也有個妹妹的說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕世美女  阿市！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:11.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐  姐姐大人…這究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.06,0:05:14.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你嫁出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:19.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天開始你就是淺井長政的夫人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:23.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你們幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.00,0:05:26.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.25,0:05:28.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:30.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真過分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是欺詐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:33.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不被發現就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:35.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你可糊弄不了我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.11,0:05:36.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.99,0:05:41.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們約好了打下美濃就給我美少女作為獎勵的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:42.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:46.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不給我的話  我就不幹活咯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:47.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.81,0:05:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我美少女啦  美少女！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.51,0:05:52.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求我這麼無聊的事情  你真不要臉啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:53.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少廢話！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:58.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人拼命的理由  只有那個吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.59,0:06:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:02.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天下第一的美少女哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.27,0:06:04.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會遵守約定的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚洗乾淨給我等著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:21.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰呢  是誰呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:26.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我的胸部…那麼好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.00,0:06:33.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向姐姐撒嬌  給100分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.43,0:06:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良前輩  請對我溫柔點哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.87,0:06:44.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個都很讚！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.39,0:06:48.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這裡果然應該是要高嶺之花…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.66,0:06:49.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,義元妹妹！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.49,0:06:56.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難  難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:06:57.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會是信奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.51,0:06:59.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.13,0:07:01.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她根本就對我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.21,0:07:02.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:05.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.79,0:07:10.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…為什麼我要給猴子糟蹋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.65,0:07:14.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要滿懷感激地  接受獎勵哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:17.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是天下第一的美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.84,0:07:20.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟  糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.59,0:07:22.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心  心理準備還…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.56,0:07:28.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人說要獎勵你  猴子大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.43,0:07:31.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:35.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天下第一的美少女  寧寧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.99,0:07:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天開始就來當猴子大人的妹妹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.33,0:07:41.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高興吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.80,0:07:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那傢伙…！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:48.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺詐啊——！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.19,0:07:55.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和淺井長政結盟的信奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:07:57.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始向南近江進軍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.64,0:08:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒了六角承禎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.82,0:08:03.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逼近了京都
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.64,0:08:16.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了這個陣容  京都就近在咫尺了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:18.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前進！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:33.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想來看看京都裡的美女  結果完全變成荒涼之地了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.00,0:08:35.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  來人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.31,0:08:37.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.81,0:08:43.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大白天的就入室搶劫嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.74,0:08:45.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是三好軍的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.69,0:08:48.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就他們嗎  怎麼看都像山賊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.87,0:08:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾開滾開
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.97,0:08:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為幕府倒臺了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.65,0:08:55.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京都已經成了無法之地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.14,0:08:58.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信奈讓我們來打探是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.07,0:09:00.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是想確認今天的日本中心…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了統治者的國家的樣子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.99,0:09:07.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.47,0:09:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和五右衛門先去收集情報
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:16.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良晴先生你們請去姬巫女大人所在的大和御所看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:17.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬巫女？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.19,0:09:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬巫女大人是站在大和的頂點的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.93,0:09:26.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說是創建這個國家的諸神的子孫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.95,0:09:28.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人崇拜供奉著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.78,0:09:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我所在的世界  似乎有微妙的不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:42.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次別想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧  沒受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.58,0:09:51.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.51,0:09:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子有一種不可思議的氣質呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.50,0:09:57.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:09:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:02.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是離開這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.79,0:10:15.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:18.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然敢去襲擊御所
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.65,0:10:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會輕易放過你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.61,0:10:23.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關白  近衛前久
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:28.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在暗中操縱公家和政治的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.29,0:10:30.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.17,0:10:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些鼠輩已經被砍頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:37.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下賤者的人頭誰要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:38.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.16,0:10:40.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬巫女大人到底去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.92,0:10:44.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧你們還是三好三人眾  這可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.44,0:10:48.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堺之豪商  津田宗及
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.43,0:10:51.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了錢什麼都肯做的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.39,0:10:54.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易打倒了將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.76,0:10:56.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生這種事  連一文都沒賺到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.97,0:11:00.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨敵退散  南蠻覆滅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.27,0:11:04.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,統領比叡山的正覺院豪盛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.63,0:11:07.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把南蠻人當作仇敵的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.94,0:11:11.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要從南蠻人手裡保護這個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.01,0:11:14.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必須由我們來掌權
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.06,0:11:17.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此我們必須要有姬巫女大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:20.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  近衛大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.65,0:11:23.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  你肯出面了啊  彈正
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.38,0:11:29.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松永彈正久秀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:32.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫不在乎地反覆倒戈和謀反
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.66,0:11:34.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是戰國的魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.44,0:11:40.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我們來說姬巫女大人是重要的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.48,0:11:46.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箕作城也攻下了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.97,0:11:48.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狀態不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.71,0:11:51.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然想到對所有的城池進行同時攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.51,0:11:54.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六角一定嚇呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.74,0:11:57.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這裡有很多優秀的武將嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.76,0:11:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有空跟他一點點耗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.81,0:12:02.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可以說是妙策  95分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.27,0:12:08.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良前輩  現在一定為立不了功而不爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:11.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的  京都那邊比較重要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.32,0:12:14.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來似乎很混亂的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.12,0:12:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在擔心嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:19.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才…才沒有！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.22,0:12:20.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半兵衛和五右衛門也在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.72,0:12:22.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒  沒問題的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.01,0:12:27.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點  解決掉六角去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.96,0:12:44.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:53.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真無法想像這裡就是京都
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.55,0:12:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的世界不是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.20,0:13:00.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要靠近我  卑賤之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.83,0:13:03.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們嘗嘗必殺奧義
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.63,0:13:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵天丸亦當如此強力劍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.24,0:13:10.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.61,0:13:11.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:16.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了  西洋修女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.76,0:13:20.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金髮和巨乳的組合  破壞力太強了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.53,0:13:22.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.06,0:13:25.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦是不能通過暴力治癒的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.81,0:13:30.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起祈禱吧  給予你的敵人愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:34.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就來好好地愛一下你的敵人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.03,0:13:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿  我還是第一次騎大洋馬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.08,0:13:40.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.44,0:13:43.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.85,0:13:47.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為日本之民  要知道羞恥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.62,0:13:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.42,0:13:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼給我滾開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.32,0:14:00.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯嘛  我梵天丸也不會輸給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:15.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找～到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.58,0:14:20.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.45,0:14:24.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是葡萄牙來的傳教士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲·弗洛伊斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.46,0:14:28.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是相良良晴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.57,0:14:29.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬千代
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:31.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是破壞的大魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.88,0:14:34.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,默示錄裡的野獸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:36.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵天丸是也
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.86,0:14:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.32,0:14:41.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你們真不走運呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:43.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來京都傳教的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.85,0:14:44.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.89,0:14:47.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平時我都在堺的南蠻寺裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:51.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想來朝廷請求在全國傳教的許可
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.36,0:14:54.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不過被拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:56.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被拒絕了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.68,0:15:01.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  他們說西洋人不能靠近御所
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:02.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真過分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.31,0:15:06.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很想見見姬巫女大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:08.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.38,0:15:11.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想同樣是侍奉神的姬巫女大人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許會理解我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.06,0:15:16.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終結戰亂之世
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.03,0:15:20.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓國家變得安居樂業
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.55,0:15:22.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是神的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.22,0:15:25.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  那也是我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.13,0:15:29.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想會實現的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.44,0:15:32.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良晴先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.18,0:15:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想只要不放棄就會實現
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然會讓人感覺很幼稚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.93,0:15:41.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我是對此深信不疑的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.09,0:15:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我也相信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.26,0:15:48.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的只有觀音寺城了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.29,0:15:50.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口氣攻下它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.39,0:15:53.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  還是勸他們來投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.28,0:15:56.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不認為他們會答應的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.50,0:15:58.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不願意投降的話  就放他們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.14,0:16:00.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必去追
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.88,0:16:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是讓他們逃跑嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.28,0:16:03.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.80,0:16:07.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是符合公主殿下的風格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:10.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事根本是聞所未聞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.27,0:16:13.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我們能成功上洛就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.50,0:16:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有必要做出無謂的流血犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.13,0:16:19.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六角那個蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.59,0:16:26.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是戰至最後一人  拖住織田信奈就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六角大人會不會逃到甲賀的深山裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.83,0:16:32.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼淒慘也該有個限度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:37.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,統治著越前的朝倉義景
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.53,0:16:40.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被稱作名門的大大名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.78,0:16:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然讓傻瓜公主上洛  這世道也算走到頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.63,0:16:51.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡將今川義元那樣的鄉下大名輔佐為將軍  才是原本的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:53.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,義元啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.14,0:16:59.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何也要得到那位公主  並添加到余的作品中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.60,0:17:02.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的興趣還真是沒變啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.54,0:17:09.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不知道是哪裡的笨蛋讓足利將軍的妹妹逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:10.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想愚弄我們嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.04,0:17:16.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要是有意見的話  就把越前七十五萬石的朝倉當作對手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.64,0:17:20.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內訌可沒有任何好處啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.83,0:17:22.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.84,0:17:26.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三好和朝倉  再加上武田和上杉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.70,0:17:29.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能形成信奈包圍網了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.87,0:17:32.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是完成這個是需要花時間的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:35.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信奈上洛的速度應該更快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:41.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫且先撤兵  在京都周圍燃起大火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:46.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信奈花時間滅火的話  余的士兵和武田、上杉家就能趕過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就交給你們了  三好三人眾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.10,0:17:51.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要…要由我們來迎擊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.31,0:17:54.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有松永彈正
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全軍要拼死與信奈戰鬥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.47,0:17:59.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.34,0:18:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,余也會伸出援手的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:08.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對信奈恨之入骨的男人  也來助一臂之力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.18,0:18:25.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是快點回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.96,0:18:28.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是京都最糟糕的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:31.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想親眼看一看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.14,0:18:32.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.11,0:18:40.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論百姓如何悲歎痛苦  不出來看一看是不知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.08,0:18:47.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先暫且不說未來  這個地獄是現在真實存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:51.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說  她知道我是來自未來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.54,0:18:56.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百姓們能夠歡聲笑語的世界會來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.73,0:19:02.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然會來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.02,0:19:04.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何能夠斷言？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.95,0:19:06.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有織田信奈在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:10.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信奈奪取天下之後  會創造一個嶄新的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:12.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織田信奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:13.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.28,0:19:18.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都歡笑著  和弗洛伊斯姐姐一樣的西洋人做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.09,0:19:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何人都能和平生活的世界  信奈一定能創造出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.04,0:19:24.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是信奈的夢想嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信奈的夢想也是大家的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.49,0:19:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  只要不放棄的話  夢想終會成真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.29,0:19:34.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.64,0:19:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.64,0:19:40.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.19,0:19:49.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭…頭有點暈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.31,0:20:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松永彈正  前來迎接您
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.78,0:20:06.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是來帶我回去的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.67,0:20:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就當作是你被無禮之徒強行帶著到處跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.01,0:20:15.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准對他們動手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.56,0:20:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老老實實跟你回去  這樣就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.83,0:20:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:37.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.48,0:20:40.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於找到你了  相良氏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:43.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五右衛門  半兵衛妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.52,0:20:49.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個氣息…是被鬼魂什麼的襲擊了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.07,0:20:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:20:53.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:55.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.37,0:21:01.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的送到這裡就行了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.44,0:21:02.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你幫忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.98,0:21:11.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個不可思議的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.78,0:21:13.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是住在這裡的巫女嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.55,0:21:19.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良晴  這次玩得很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.27,0:21:22.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朕由衷地表示感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.75,0:21:25.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朕？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.98,0:21:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬…巫女殿下？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.42,0:21:35.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是  織田信奈終於完成了上洛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.53,0:21:40.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京都成為織田家所統治的區域
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.52,0:21:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照你說的  我讓京都的治安恢復正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:48.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像相當嚴重呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.99,0:21:52.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這樣應該就會好一些了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.61,0:21:53.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.72,0:21:55.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是做了應該做的事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.15,0:21:58.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕的地方還有很多很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.37,0:22:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是我奪取天下之前罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.62,0:22:07.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  信奈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.85,0:22:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.75,0:22:12.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創造一個和平的國家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.79,0:22:16.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,====================================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.18,0:22:35.29,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ただ  時代の真ん中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.52,0:22:40.67,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}立たされて  戸惑う時に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.81,0:22:46.11,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}手を引いてくれた人へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.25,0:22:50.34,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}出来ること探した
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.57,0:22:55.77,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}傷つきながら  笑う姿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.92,0:23:00.96,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の裏  涙が見えた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.13,0:23:06.35,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}救い求める声  聴き取れるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.61,0:23:12.45,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}許された者だけ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.95,0:23:17.72,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}数え切れぬ  嵐を越えて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.83,0:23:23.31,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたの闇  裂くヒカリになる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.44,0:23:28.47,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}もう  迷わない  ともに生きたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.60,0:23:33.90,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誓う夢が  どんな無謀であっても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.03,0:23:43.70,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}おぼえていて  信じられる場所は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.84,0:23:47.40,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ここにあると
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.18,0:22:35.29,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只是深陷時代紛爭的漩渦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.52,0:22:40.67,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無奈佇立  獨自彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.81,0:22:46.11,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一直在尋覓著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.25,0:22:50.34,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}生命中不可或缺的那個他
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.57,0:22:55.77,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}堅韌的外表  寂寞的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.92,0:23:00.96,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}掩藏不住內心幽然淚下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.13,0:23:06.35,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}彷彿能聆聽到救贖之音的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.61,0:23:12.45,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只有尋覓著的他
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.95,0:23:17.72,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}經歷風花雪月的洗禮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.83,0:23:23.31,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}方知孤影的你似流光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.44,0:23:28.47,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不再猶豫  願與你同存
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.60,0:23:33.90,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就算誓言之夢的前方是一片迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.03,0:23:43.70,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}請記住  屬於你的歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.84,0:23:47.40,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就在此處
